      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8fa0de68-258a-11e1-ae7f-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
