        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-01-31 23:15:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: (1 inline comment)\n\nAlex, this needs to be rebased to take into account the changes Liang made for multiple OIs, and to fix the other issues unrelated to FID-on-OST.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
