      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f69f53e4-7146-11e1-a89e-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 15 tests.  4 tests failed: replay-dual, replay-single, sanityn, sanity.",
