        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-03-18 23:28:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe reason I'd like to make it a per-group constant is that we might want to change the number of subdirs for new sequence numbers without having to rehash the existing directories.\n\nThis is an extra, so I don't think we need to implement this.  I was thinking it would make sense if we do an index iteration to find the actual existing subdirs rather than just guessing at the number of directories.  The current structure of the code was not set up well to do that.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
